        <div class="wwf-phs-border ">
          <h1>Climate change</h1>
          <p><p>Climate change affects every corner of our planet – from the poles to the tropics, from the mountains to the oceans. Many of the world's biggest challenges, from poverty to wildlife extinction, are made more difficult by climate change.</p><p>We have the knowledge and the tools – we just need politicians to lead the way.</p></p>


          

          <div class="btn-wrap">
                          
                   

