  <section id="places-affected-by-climate-change" class="slider-slice_container paragraph-container">
    <section class="square-carousel-landscape " aria-labelledby="carousel-heading">
      <div class="article_wrapper square-landscape-heading-container">
                <h3>
          Places affected by climate change
        </h3>
                        <p>
          <p>From fragile mangrove swamps in India to the fast-decreasing icy wilderness of the Arctic to the vast oceans, the delicate balance of life in precious places all over the world is being put under stress.</p>

        </p>
              </div>

